S.FORM: Forest Able nalecuhan i American, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Forest Able i 1976 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ku uwac atu silsil 20, namapili' tu nu Syracuse Nationals putiput putiput. 7 bulad 27 demiad, 1932 a mihca, Forest Able, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
